channel.title: Vision - Produk (Tome Rework/Remix)
channel.description:
hey guys ! i present my 2- track remix/rework of produk's vision !
the first track is the original beat with my vocals on it, and the second one is my own take on it !
shoutout to @Produk for creating this masterpiece ! listen to it [here](https://soundcloud.com/melodiesbytome/sets/vision2) and let me know what you think !
(sorry for being cringey idk how to talk to people and stuff lol)
